      <h2 id="thoughts-on-remembrance-and-peace">Thoughts on Remembrance and Peace</h2>
      <p></p>
<p>These messages emphasize the importance of remembering the departed and finding peace.</p>
<li> May your memories of him/her bring you comfort.</li>
<li> Cherish the beautiful memories you shared.</li>
<li> May his/her soul rest in peace and Jannatul Firdous.</li>
<li> Remembering your loved one with love and respect.</li>
<li> May the beautiful memories you have bring you solace.</li>
<li> May his/her spirit live on in your hearts.</li>
<li> May Allah grant him/her a peaceful afterlife.</li>
